se.cbb.jprime.topology

Class LeafLeafMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.cbb.jprime.topology.LeafLeafMap

  • public class LeafLeafMap
extends java.lang.Object
    Very simple map linking each leaf in a guest topology G to its leaf in a host topology S. Assumes that this mapping will never change, and is therefore not a Dependent. See also MPRMap.
